description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'Core Burn Express Pilates' from the channel Christie Wang.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Groove Session vibe.
The The Groove Session vibe means Fun, fluid, expressive, completely in the moment. This is especially good for Days when you want to move intuitively and just vibe..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Strengthen and stretch your core with Christie and Laine while listening to a playlist of recent pop hits. ...
